messages.speech:
Free and discounted software is available to currently-enrolled, credit-based students, staff and faculty only.

To access the reduced software and/or hardware purchasing page, log in to the myCentury. (https://my.century.edu/) Click Students > Technology > Free & Discounted Software.

Century College's IT Services department is continually working with vendors to offer additional reduced-cost options, so it's worthwhile to check back often!

Many retailers also offer educational discounts:
    Adobe: http://www.academicsuperstore.com/products/Adobe?cat=1&uumc=550517&utm_source=search&utm_medium=paidsearch&sissr=1
    Apple: https://www.apple.com/us-hed/shop?aid=Edu-IntSearch-B
    HP: http://store.hp.com/?jumpid=re_r11662_redirect_ETR
    Dell: http://www.dell.com/en-us/learn/purchaseprogram/university?c=us&l=en&s=eep&link_number=17970622
    Lenovo: https://www3.lenovo.com/us/en/landingpage/students-and-teachers/
